      "file_path": "kubernetes/dmaap/components/dmaap-dr-prov/resources/feeds/DefaultPM.json",
      "patchset_number": 4,
      "line": 18,
      "message": "Assuming dcae-pm-mapper is the service name, then I think we should also assume that DR Node can deliver to it.  In this case, we are using dcaeLocation \"san-francisco\" as a place holder for some central k8s location.  We know that dr-node will be in that k8s location.\nIn the future, dcae-pm-mapper may need to be at an edge k8s.  But a dr-node instance should be there too.  So again, the (local) service name should be sufficient for delivery.\nThe problem remains for DR to figure out how to know to get a file to a specific edge dr-node for that delivery, of course.",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 1111,
        "name": "Dominic Lunanuova",
        "display_name": null,
        "email": "dgl@research.att.com",
        "username": "dglFromAtt"
      },
